name: White Label Project 2012 Winter Classic
additionalNotes:
As is common with Viaje, the blend is a Nicaraguan puro with a Corojo wrapper made at the Fábrica de Tabacos Raíces Cubanas S. de R.L. factory in Danlí, Honduras. Viaje will release 250 bundles of 25 cigars (6,250 total cigars), the largest WLP release to date. The cigars will carry a MSRP of $8.00 or $200.00 per bundle.

From Andre:  "I blended WC with the colder states in mind. I wanted something on the smaller side that delivered flavor without being overpowering. These are medium plus."
